-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-purple-100 py-12 mt-12\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Explore These Cities</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">This article mentions the following cities. Discover dog parks and resources in these locations.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white text-purple-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors font-medium shadow-sm\" href=\"/cities/erie\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt mr-2\"></i>Erie</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white text-purple-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors font-medium shadow-sm\" href=\"/cities/allen-tx\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt mr-2\"></i>Allen</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-white text-purple-700 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors font-medium shadow-sm\" href=\"/cities/spring-tx\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt mr-2\"></i>Spring</a></div></div></div></div><footer class=\"footer-new\"><div class=\"footer-container\"><div class=\"footer-grid\"><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">IndoorDogPark</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/about\">About us</a></li><li><a href=\"/partners\">Partners</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Discover</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/\">Browse parks</a></li><li><a href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a></li><li><a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Park Owners</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a></li><li><a href=\"/owner-resources\">Owner resources</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Support</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1