:\\\"Indoor dog park in columbus\\\"},\\\"alt_text\\\":\\\"indoor-dog-park-in-columbus\\\",\\\"media_type\\\":\\\"image\\\",\\\"mime_type\\\":\\\"image/jpeg\\\",\\\"media_details\\\":{\\\"width\\\":1344,\\\"height\\\":768,\\\"file\\\":\\\"4-best-indoor-dog-parks-in-columbus-ohio.jpg\\\",\\\"sizes\\\":{\\\"large\\\":{\\\"file\\\":\\\"4-best-indoor-dog-parks-in-columbus-ohio-large.jpg\\\",\\\"width\\\":1200,\\\"height\\\":686,\\\"mime_type\\\":\\\"image/jpeg\\\",\\\"source_url\\\":\\\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/73ac3d6cd5a6b7e2764d01ea511f749c0a1341c9-1344x768.webp?w=1200\\\"},\\\"medium\\\":{\\\"file\\\":\\\"4-best-indoor-dog-parks-in-columbus-ohio-medium.jpg\\\",\\\"width\\\":800,\\\"height\\\":457,\\\"mime_type\\\":\\\"image/jpeg\\\",\\\"source_url\\\":\\\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/73ac3d6cd5a6b7e2764d01ea511f749c0a1341c9-1344x768.webp?w=800\\\"}}},\\\"source_url\\\":\\\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/ruuprk8g/production/73ac3d6cd5a6b7e2764d01ea511f749c0a1341c9-1344x768.webp?w=1200\\\"},\\\"link\\\":\\\"/blog/4-best-indoor-dog-parks-in-columbus-ohio\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"publish\\\",\\\"commentStatus\\\":\\\"open\\\"}}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"3c:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"ChIJ3Xa7vli_VogRFUqUnpwdMSA\\\",{\\\"park\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ChIJ3Xa7vli_VogRFUqUnpwdMSA\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Park\\\",\\\"businessType\\\":\\\"Indoor Dog Park\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Pet owners in Gastonia find Dog Park to be a solid choice. This facility features modern training facilities, North Carolina pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, climate-controlled environment. conveniently located in the heart of Gastonia. Discover why Gastonia pet parents choose Dog Park\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"dog-park\\\",\\\"address\\\":\\\"Lowell\\\",\\\"street\\\":\\\"Lowell\\\",\\\"city\\\":\\\"Gastonia\\\",\\\"state\\\":\\\"NC\\\",\\\"zipCode\\\":\\\"28056\\\",\\\"full_address\\\":\\\"Lowell, NC 28